  <h2>What is the scenario for this case study?</h2>

  <p>
    A user reports they can no longer access the Linux server. Their password doesn't work and nobody changed it. What happened? In this article we investigate the incident step by step using Wazuh's <strong>Threat Hunting</strong> and <strong>Discover</strong> panels.
  </p>

  <!-- Video del curso bloqueado -->
